metadata.description: The Rich ape yatch club collection features 5000 unique characters. No two Rich ape yatch club are exactly alike, and each of them can be officially owned by a single person on the blockchain. Rich ape yatch club is one of the newest examples of the Fungible Token in Ethereum and was the inspiration for the ERC-721A standard that powers most digital art and collectibles. Join a determined group of ever-growing individuals Each Rich ape yatch club resides on the Ethereum blockchain as a unique, non-fungible token (NFT) comprised of a unique combination of traits and underlying DNAs. Through this marketplace you can buy, bid and offer Rich ape yatch club sale.
